title: Week 11 Studs & Duds + Monday Punday, Rapid Cold Takes - Fantasy Football Podcast for 11/22
description:
The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode! On today’s fantasy football podcast, get a recap of the biggest Studs & Duds of Week 11! Jonathan Taylor and Austin Ekeler headline the studs, with fantasy duds Patrick Mahomes and Dak Prescott combining for zero passing touchdowns! Plus, injury updates and Monday Punday! Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for November 22nd, 2021.
  
 (04:45) - Monday Punday
 (07:55) - NFL News 
 (19:05) - Fantasy Studmuffins
 (19:15) - RB Studs
 (29:45) - QB Studs

 (42:40) - TE Studs
 (44:45) - Fantasy Duds
 (44:50) - QB Duds
 (51:10) - RB Duds
